Package: makedatar
Title: Load and Prepare Clinical Trial Data from Column-Info Excel Workbooks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Shimpei", "Morimoto", email = "your@email.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a pipeline for importing, transforming, and cleaning
    clinical trial datasets driven by a col_info schema table stored in an
    Excel workbook. The col_info table declares variable roles (ID, exposure,
    background, outcome, time-to-event), transformation rules, cutoff-based
    discretisation, factor labels, and stratum-inclusion filters. The package
    converts the original script-based makedata_01.R workflow into composable,
    testable functions with no global-state side effects.
